No one's going to say anything?

38
00:02:26,851 --> 00:02:28,312
Who's feeling the guilt?

39
00:02:30,212 --> 00:02:31,592
How stupid can one be?

40
00:02:33,172 --> 00:02:34,640
Why are you people
still standing around?

41
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,771
Are you waiting for me

42
00:02:35,772 --> 00:02:37,192
to invite you to your desk one by one?

43
