Guan Xingxin is on medical leave.

44
00:02:50,571 --> 00:02:52,232
You'll take over her topic.

45
00:02:52,811 --> 00:02:53,871
Submit it to me

46
00:02:54,371 --> 00:02:56,151
with the updated materials
for re-approval.

47
00:02:56,571 --> 00:02:57,352
Also,

48
00:02:57,772 --> 00:02:59,352
