Just speak your mind.

52
00:03:10,131 --> 00:03:13,072
I thought you didn't like Guan Xingxin.

53
00:03:13,292 --> 00:03:14,871
I didn't expect you'd back her up.

54
00:03:15,332 --> 00:03:16,671
Those are two different things.

55
00:03:16,932 --> 00:03:18,312
Haven't you heard of this saying?

56
00:03:18,851 --> 00:03:20,711
The person who started the fire
is the heretic,

57
00:03:20,851 --> 00:03:22,111
not the one who got burned.

58
00:03:23,172 --> 00:03:24,271
Shakespeare.

59
00:03:26,292 --> 00:03:27,551
Not bad.

60
00:03:27,732 --> 00:03:28,451
I guess

61
