Remember him?

67
00:03:38,612 --> 00:03:39,831
Your new colleague,

68
00:03:40,052 --> 00:03:41,551
the person-in-charge
of the new column.

69
00:04:09,571 --> 00:04:11,151
Why didn't you answer my calls?

70
00:04:17,932 --> 00:04:18,912
My phone is off.

71
00:04:19,172 --> 00:04:20,232
I wanted some peace.

72
00:04:21,011 --> 00:04:22,152
Shen just left.

73
00:04:23,412 --> 00:04:24,871
Your mom called me.

74
00:04:28,211 --> 00:04:29,272
Which one?

75
00:04:38,771 --> 00:04:39,832
It's not your fault.

76
00:04:40,952 --> 00:04:42,000
Don't be so hard on yourself.

77
00:05:04,571 --> 00:05:05,712
Liang Daiwen.

78
00:05:09,331 --> 00:05:12,111
Do you know the amount of news
I've received today?

79
00:05:15,331 --> 00:05:17,671
You're the only person
who said that to me.

80
00:05:22,331 --> 00:05:25,431
At the beginning,
I really didn't know he was married.

81
00:05:25,652 --> 00:05:28,751
When I found out,
we had already broken up.

82
00:05:29,612 --> 00:05:31,631
I don't know why

83
00:05:31,652 --> 00:05:33,952
no one is willing to accept
my side of the story.

84
00:05:43,292 --> 00:05:44,010
You knew

85
00:05:44,011 --> 00:05:45,792
how the Internet operates
when you chose to stream.

86
00:05:46,691 --> 00:05:48,232
There's no need to get stuck in a rut

87
00:05:48,972 --> 00:05:50,311
or put yourself down.

88
00:05:58,691 --> 00:06:00,111
This will pass.

89
00:06:21,063 --> 00:06:25,478
